                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180218-119-victim752 t18180218-119-viclabel638"></join>, and lives in <placeName id="t18180218-119-crimeloc639">Oxford-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18180218-119-crimeloc639" type="placeName" value="Oxford-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18180218-119-crimeloc639" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180218-119-off636 t18180218-119-crimeloc639"></join>. On the 30th of January, between seven and eight o'clock in the evening, I saw a young man come into the shop, take up the flannel, and giveit to the prisoner, who ran away with it. I pursued, calling out Stop thief! - He threw it down - I collared him. I am sure he is the man.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
